# Allowlist, not denylist: the image build only needs the Go module and the
# sources `go build ./server/cmd/lore` actually imports. Excluding everything
# else keeps the build context small and stops edits to the SDKs, docs, spec, or
# CI from invalidating the `COPY . .` layer cache. Self-maintaining as new
# top-level siblings are added.
*
!go.mod
!go.sum
!core
!server
